verbose_text: 14 Fibulin-3 also stimulates certain tissue inhibitor of metalloproteinases (TIMP-1 and TIMP-3), and inhibits the matrix metalloproteinases (MMP2, MMP-3, and MMP-9) all involved in the remodeling and pathogenesis of OA.
